Weekly wiki lint for this Obsidian vault. Bounded tasks only:
1. DUPLICATES: find pairs of pages covering the same topic (same subject, overlapping content). Merge only clear duplicates: keep the better page, move the other's unique content in, replace the loser with a one-line redirect stub linking to the survivor. Max 10 merges per run.
2. CONTRADICTIONS: find pages making conflicting claims about the same thing (dates, statuses, verdicts). Do NOT resolve — list them in ops/contradictions.md with wikilinks and one line each on the conflict. Never collapse divergent readings.
3. ORPHANS: list pages with zero inbound wikilinks (excluding _archive, raw) in ops/orphans.md.
4. STALE STATUS: pages whose status labels (in progress, blocked, next) are older than 30 days — list in ops/stale-status.md.
5. Append a summary line to ops/maintenance-log.md, then git add -A && git commit -m 'weekly lint 2026-07-03'. Do not push.
